response.overview: This all-1960s video featured two dozen clips of gyrations and grinding, with a little dancing and outdoor fun thrown in for good measure. A psychedelic rainbow of blondes, brunettes, and sweet Sixties soul sisters press their bed sheets pelvically as they trip out for the camera. The highlight of the album is a color clip of a perky madras-clad chick posing both indoors and beside a peaceful lake.
response.title: Nudie Cuties: Volume 9
